videos.description: Iowa quarterback Nate Stanley throws a fastball to tight end T.J. Hockenson for a three-yard touchdown to put the Hawkeyes on the board first.
videos.headline: Iowa QB fires 3-yard TD strike

videos.description: Iowa quarterback Nate Stanley eludes pressure, steps up in the pocket, and whips a strike to a wide-open Ihmir Smith-Marsette for a 60-yard catch-and-run touchdown.
videos.headline: Iowa QB gets crafty in pocket, throws 60-yard TD

videos.description: Minnesota quarterback Zack Annexstad hits Rashod Bateman on a pretty back-shoulder throw for a 3-yard touchdown. Bateman was graced with the Golden Gophers' touchdown fedora on the sidelines following his score.
videos.headline: Minnesota WR snags 3-yard TD, rewarded with fedora

videos.description: Iowa's T.J. Hockenson receives the direct snap and follows a convoy of blockers into the end zone for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Iowa's bizarre direct snap works out for 4-yard TD

videos.description: Minnesota's Carter Coughlin strips Nate Stanley deep in Iowa territory, setting up a 1-yard wildcat touchdown for Seth Green and the Golden Gophers.
videos.headline: Minnesota's forced fumble leads to TD

videos.description: Iowa quarterback Nate Stanley stays cool in the pocket and zips a five-yard touchdown to Noah Fant, extending the Hawkeyes' lead.
videos.headline: Iowa's Stanley flips 5-yard TD pass

videos.description: Minnesota quarterback Zack Annexstad attempts a deep ball and is picked off by Riley Moss, setting up a field goal on the ensuing drive for Iowa.
videos.headline: Minnesota QB airmails interception

videos.description: Zack Annexstad sells the triple-option fake and throws a strike to Rashod Bateman for a seven-yard touchdown, cutting the Golden Gophers' deficit to 10.
videos.headline: Minnesota clawing back with 7-yard TD pass

videos.description: T.J. Hockenson hauls in a 30-yard gain, setting up Mekhi Sargent's two-yard touchdown to ice the game the Iowa.
videos.headline: Iowa ices game with 30-yard pass, setting up short TD
